00:16:21,230 --> 00:16:23,780
Sorry, please queue up.

246
00:16:27,860 --> 00:16:29,410
You go first.

247
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:31,770
I'm looking for Doctor Bai.

248
00:16:31,770 --> 00:16:33,160
You mean Doctor Bai Zhu?

249
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:36,940
So that character is pronounced 'Zhu'? Yes, I think that's him.

250
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:38,910
I'll ask for you.

251
00:16:40,130 --> 00:16:44,390
Doctor Bai, there is a lady looking for you in triage.

252
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:46,330
Excuse me, your name is...?

253
00:16:46,330 --> 00:16:48,690
Li Xuan.

254
00:16:48,690 --> 00:16:51,120
She said she is called Li Xuan.

255
00:16:52,250 --> 00:16:53,920
I see.

256
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:57,000
Doctor Bai wants you to wait for him at the clinic.

257
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,510
Thank you.

258
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:05,690
Sorry, I forgot to ask. Where is his clinic?

259
00:17:05,690 --> 00:17:07,670
Go straight ahead and then turn right, you'll see the clinic.

260
00:17:07,670 --> 00:17:10,170
Ok, thank you.

261
00:17:14,170 --> 00:17:15,940
Excuse me, what's wrong.

262
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:19,420
Doctor, it's my insomnia...

263
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:21,420
Wait a moment.

264
00:17:25,130 --> 00:17:28,900
You are...Li Xuan?

265
00:17:28,900 --> 00:17:31,400
You're pretty handsome, Doctor Bai.

266
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:34,670
- Have you seen your mother? 
 - Do you have a girlfriend?

267
00:17:34,670 --> 00:17:37,560
Let's talk about your mother's illness.

268
00:17:37,560 --> 00:17:40,580
No need, you set it all out in your email.

269
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:42,970
Did you want me to come and say my final farewells?

270
00:17:42,970 --> 00:17:45,930
You're mother won't accept treatment or surgery.

271
00:17:45,930 --> 00:17:49,940
But, there is a great chance of success with this surgery. I want you to persuade her.

272
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:51,650
Don't put your hopes in me.

273
00:17:51,650 --> 00:17:53,210
She won't listen to me.

274
00:17:53,210 --> 00:17:54,750
But you are her daughter.

275
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:58,210
Doctor Bai, you don't seem to understand your patient.

276
00:17:58,210 --> 00:18:01,650
Of course, biologically speaking I am her daughter.

277
00:18:01,650 --> 00:18:07,290
But for her, I'm just a way to get revenge on my father.

278
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:10,270
You'd better think of something else.

279
00:18:10,980 --> 00:18:14,060
You came all this way, why don't you go and see her.

280
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:17,410
Who knows when your next chance will be.

281
00:18:27,900 --> 00:18:30,670
Ms Ge, here is some hot water.

282
00:18:39,420 --> 00:18:42,450
It's boiling. How can I drink this?

283
00:18:42,450 --> 00:18:45,540
Sorry. I will go and get some cooler water.

284
00:18:45,540 --> 00:18:49,360
Young Miss! When did you get back?

285
00:18:56,610 --> 00:18:58,770
Why are you dressed like that?

286
00:18:59,450 --> 00:19:01,840
I guess its genetic.

287
00:19:01,840 --> 00:19:04,600
Why are you staying here? It doesn't seem to suit your tastes.

288
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:09,370
Weren't you happy studying in the UK? Why did you come back?

289
00:19:11,250 --> 00:19:12,330
Does your father know?

290
00:19:12,330 --> 00:19:15,830
I heard you are ill. I thought I should at least show my face.

291
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:19,070
Or else all the doctors and nurses would think you have no family or friends.

292
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:21,300
I'm fine.

293
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:23,490
You can go back.

294
00:19:23,490 --> 00:19:27,380
Makes sense. I'm off then. Take care.

295
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:28,750
Young Miss, let me walk you out.

296
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:31,930
No need. Stay and take care of her.

297
00:19:31,930 --> 00:19:33,670
Bye!

298
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:39,670
Doctor Bai, you see what I mean, right?

299
00:19:39,670 --> 00:19:41,910
I can't help you with her.

300
00:19:41,910 --> 00:19:44,020
- Bye. 
 - Wait.

301
00:19:44,930 --> 00:19:47,130
You can't bear to let me go?

302
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:50,670
Then let's exchange numbers. We can hang out in future.

303
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:55,850
Here.

304
00:19:57,140 --> 00:19:59,610
Doctor Bai, you're so traditional.

305
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:08,320
Bye!

306
00:20:13,550 --> 00:20:15,120
Who was that?

307
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:18,940
Li Xuan. Ge Xue Hong's daughter.

308
00:20:18,940 --> 00:20:21,290
She's Li Xuan?

309
00:20:21,290 --> 00:20:23,400
So hot.

310
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:26,210
You're so rude.

311
00:20:30,860 --> 00:20:33,350
Did Ge Xue Hong agree to the surgery?

312
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:37,520
They have a unique mother-daughter relationship.

313
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:43,930
Aren't you getting on well with her assistant?

314
00:20:43,930 --> 00:20:46,050
Yes.

315
00:20:46,050 --> 00:20:48,770
I wanted to keep it discreet, but I can't help it.

316
00:20:48,770 --> 00:20:50,790
It's so tough.

317
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:56,270
- What are you trying? 
 - You guess.

318
00:20:56,270 --> 00:21:01,450
She said when Li Xuan was 10 years old, her mother send her abroad by herself.

319
00:21:01,450 --> 00:21:05,170
Even her husband didn't know where Li Xuan was.

320
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:08,060
Li Xuan felt like she was abandoned.

321
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:10,740
So her relationship with her mother has been very frosty.

322
00:21:10,740 --> 00:21:13,120
They only call a few times a year, and she rarely comes back to China.

323
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:17,760
Did she say why Ge Xue Hong sent Li Xuan away?

324
00:21:17,760 --> 00:21:19,980
She wasn't sure.

325
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:22,060
But if I was to guess,

326
00:21:22,060 --> 00:21:25,680
it must be because Li Xuan was getting in her way.

327
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:27,160
How?

328
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:29,610
Fighting over her husband with all his mistresses.

329
00:21:29,610 --> 00:21:35,040
Li Xuan said that Ge Xue Hong used her as a weapon to get revenge on her father.

330
00:21:35,040 --> 00:21:38,220
So she sent her away was to get revenge on the cheating husband.

331
00:21:38,220 --> 00:21:40,610
The purpose was to separate them,

332
00:21:40,610 --> 00:21:43,470
and not let the cheating husband see his own daughter.

333
00:21:43,470 --> 00:21:48,100
No matter how much she hated her husband, she shouldn't use her own daughter as a weapon.

334
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:51,160
Hate makes people irrational.

335
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,650
No, that can't be.

336
00:21:52,650 --> 00:21:56,320
Wasn't the reason Ge Xue Hong didn't want to get a double mastectomy

337
00:21:56,320 --> 00:22:00,090
to keep her husband's attention with her beauty. How did it become hate?

338
00:22:00,090 --> 00:22:04,830
How could such a proud person lose to mistresses?

339
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:09,240
She did it because of hate, not love.

340
00:22:10,470 --> 00:22:13,240
What a pity for her daughter.

341
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:16,580
No matter what, it seems there's no way forward for us.

342
00:22:16,580 --> 00:22:20,520
We can't solve this mother-daughter relationship.

343
00:22:20,520 --> 00:22:21,960
Not necessarily.

344
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:25,000
As I see it, they both still

345
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,540
care about each other.

346
00:22:26,540 --> 00:22:28,840
Why can't I see it?

347
00:22:28,840 --> 00:22:30,240
That's the difference between you and me.

348
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:32,420
I like your confidence.

349
00:22:32,420 --> 00:22:34,150
Keep going.

350
00:22:41,570 --> 00:22:43,790
- Do you think she's here? 
 - She should be.

351
00:22:43,790 --> 00:22:45,490
- Hi, doctors! 
 - She's here.

352
00:22:45,490 --> 00:22:47,640
And on time.

353
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,630
Let me introduce you.

354
00:22:50,630 --> 00:22:53,690
This is emergency room doctor, Xu Yi Ran.

355
00:22:53,690 --> 00:22:56,250
- This is Li Xuan, Ge Hong's daughter. 
 - Hello.

356
00:22:56,250 --> 00:22:58,090
- Nice to meet you. 
 - Nice to meet you too.

357
00:22:58,090 --> 00:23:01,810
I guess you have to be handsome to work at Tongshan Hospital.

358
00:23:01,810 --> 00:23:03,640
You are very good looking, Doctor Xu.

359
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:05,980
You have good judgement.

360
00:23:05,980 --> 00:23:09,560
Although, you still can't compete with Doctor Bai.

361
00:23:10,460 --> 00:23:15,390
Are you sure? Are you sure you don't need to see the opticians?

362
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:17,690
Alright, let's get down to business.

363
00:23:17,690 --> 00:23:19,370
Doctor Bai, why are you so serious?

364
00:23:19,370 --> 00:23:23,750
He's not serious, he's nervous around pretty girls.

365
00:23:23,750 --> 00:23:25,700
Really?

366
00:23:25,700 --> 00:23:28,720
Doctor Bai, am I pretty?

367
00:23:30,760 --> 00:23:33,070
He has a better undertsanding of aesthetics, ask him.

368
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:34,800
Doctor Xu?

369
00:23:35,560 --> 00:23:38,350
I think you very much suit my understanding of beauty.

370
00:23:39,150 --> 00:23:40,820
Take a look at this.

371
00:23:42,990 --> 00:23:46,310
Doctor Bai...I've told you already.

372
00:23:46,310 --> 00:23:48,350
I can't help you with her.

373
00:23:48,350 --> 00:23:51,450
We found these documents ourselves.

374
00:23:51,450 --> 00:23:54,990
Your mother has been donating to charity.

375
00:23:54,990 --> 00:23:59,560
Most of them are organizations to do with mother and baby or child development.

376
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:02,220
So? What are you trying to say?

377
00:24:02,220 --> 00:24:04,240
She is thinking of you.

378
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:14,470
You clearly also care for her. Why can't you admit it?

379
00:24:15,340 --> 00:24:17,900
Who do you think you are?

380
00:24:17,900 --> 00:24:20,690
I'm busy, good bye.

381
00:24:21,660 --> 00:24:23,300
See.

382
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:28,960
Even though Doctor Xiao found these documents, even if your hunch is right,

383
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:31,730
even if Li Xuan is thinking of Ge Xue Hong, so what?

384
00:24:31,730 --> 00:24:34,960
Do you really think going back to Ge Xue Hong will convince her to have the surgery?

385
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:36,880
Let's see how it goes.

386
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:38,150
Why aren't you answering the question?

387
00:24:38,150 --> 00:24:39,690
Just wait.

388
00:24:39,690 --> 00:24:43,960
Wait for our new laboratory to be built.

389
00:24:45,350 --> 00:24:48,110
Your attitude, honestly!

390
00:24:48,110 --> 00:24:51,420
You said you often drink alcohol. It might be cirrhosis.

391
00:24:51,420 --> 00:24:54,980
We can only know for sure once the CT comes back.

392
00:24:57,040 --> 00:25:00,630
I'll send you for a CT, then you can come back to see me.

393
00:25:00,630 --> 00:25:02,080
Ok.

394
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:08,010
Thank you, Doctor.

395
00:25:13,070 --> 00:25:14,970
Doctor Xiao, you seem quite busy.

396
00:25:14,970 --> 00:25:17,240
What do you want, Doctor Bai?

397
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:20,760
Thank you for the documents, they helped a lot.

398
00:25:20,760 --> 00:25:22,600
You're too modest.

399
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:25,580
I found some new documents this morning.

400
00:25:25,580 --> 00:25:30,100
They might be of use for you. When I'm free, let's discuss it?

401
00:25:30,100 --> 00:25:31,870
Sure.

402
00:25:31,870 --> 00:25:34,040
<i>[EICU]<i></i></i>

403
00:25:45,370 --> 00:25:47,690
Doctor Bai.

404
00:25:47,690 --> 00:25:52,450
Your mother just took her medication, she isn't sleeping yet, why don't you go in and say hi.

405
00:25:52,450 --> 00:25:56,590
I didn't come for her. I came to see Doctor Xu.

406
00:25:58,160 --> 00:26:01,050
Just wait here, he'll be out soon.

407
00:26:14,080 --> 00:26:15,760
What are you looking at so seriously?

408
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,830
It's a web novel Li Xuan wrote.

409
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:21,160
It was Li Xuan who wrote this web novel?

410
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:23,330
How did you find it, Doctor Xiao?

411
00:26:23,330 --> 00:26:25,790
I found the link on her Weibo.

412
00:26:25,790 --> 00:26:29,750
But this was written four years ago, when she first started university.

413
00:26:29,750 --> 00:26:33,360
Although she used a penname,

414
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:35,580
She used it to log in to literary forums.

415
00:26:35,580 --> 00:26:39,600
The personal information, date of birth and university are all the same as Li Xuan's.

416
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:41,880
But the content is key.

417
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:45,780
Whether its the parents of the main character, or their situation,

418
00:26:45,780 --> 00:26:49,350
from one glance you can tell it is about Ge Xue Hong and her husband.

419
00:26:50,020 --> 00:26:54,350
I never thought that Li Xuan would write novels.

420
00:26:54,350 --> 00:26:56,000
What did she write?

421
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:57,460
What was in her heart.

422
00:26:57,460 --> 00:26:59,750
- What was in her heart?
  - You're right.

423
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:04,500
In this novel, the main character was abandoned by her mother at a young age.

424
00:27:04,500 --> 00:27:07,500
She lived alone by herself in the UK.

425
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:10,380
But she never gave up on her desire for maternal love.

426
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:12,630
She dreamed of returning to her childhood,

427
00:27:12,630 --> 00:27:16,640
returning to her mother's embrace. Got it?

428
00:27:16,640 --> 00:27:18,120
Yes.

429
00:27:20,930 --> 00:27:22,570
Take your time.

430
00:27:28,270 --> 00:27:30,280
Doctor Bai, you're here.

431
00:27:35,140 --> 00:27:36,920
Ms Ge.

432
00:27:40,180 --> 00:27:42,190
I brought you something.

433
00:27:42,190 --> 00:27:43,370
What is it?

434
00:27:43,370 --> 00:27:45,500
A novel written by your daughter.

435
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:52,780
She can even write novels?

436
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:57,630
I would advise you to read it when you can. You might learn something.

437
00:27:57,630 --> 00:27:59,910
I'll leave it here.

438
00:27:59,910 --> 00:28:01,740
Doctor Bai!

439
00:28:04,530 --> 00:28:08,350
I know what you are trying so hard to do.

440
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:11,680
I'm asking you, don't waste your time.

441
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:13,220
I won't agree to the surgery.

442
00:28:13,220 --> 00:28:17,450
Get me an oncology as soon as possible.

443
00:28:17,450 --> 00:28:20,390
And a new treatment plan.

444
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:24,330
I almost forgot to tell you.

445
00:28:24,330 --> 00:28:26,900
When you read the book, make sure you have some tissues.

446
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:31,780
And don't get too emotional, it will affect your condition.

447
00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:54,070
<i>[Emergency]<i></i></i>

448
00:28:54,070 --> 00:28:56,690
The vital signs of the patient in bed 14 are all normal.

449
00:28:56,690 --> 00:29:00,030
I just checked her blood pressure and blood sugar, no problem there.

450
00:29:21,150 --> 00:29:22,310
<i>Going Home.<i></i></i>

451
00:29:28,280 --> 00:29:34,050
I opened my right fist and stretched out my palm.

452
00:29:34,050 --> 00:29:38,650
A deep line ran through the center of my palm.

453
00:29:38,650 --> 00:29:42,800
I used the middle finger of my left hand

454
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:46,980
to carefully trace the line from left to right.

455
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:51,420
The quiet depressions, the strong warmth,

456
00:29:51,420 --> 00:29:57,390
and a sudden overwhelming sense of vertigo.

457
00:29:57,390 --> 00:30:02,080
The book said that people with a line like mine

458
00:30:02,080 --> 00:30:04,540
will wander without a home.

459
00:30:06,380 --> 00:30:11,740
I was like wooden toy, abandoned in the corner of the prop cupboard in a huge theater.

460
00:30:11,740 --> 00:30:15,200
My face covered in dust.

461
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:18,310
Opening my dark eyes,

462
00:30:18,310 --> 00:30:22,280
I tried to hear the sound of snow falling.

463
00:30:22,940 --> 00:30:28,530
But apart from the occasional sounds of footsteps, or a bursts of applause,

464
00:30:28,530 --> 00:30:31,460
I couldn't hear a thing.

465
00:30:31,460 --> 00:30:37,220
I was there through all four seasons. Always.

466
00:30:38,210 --> 00:30:40,760
But the mother who had

467
00:30:40,760 --> 00:30:44,060
danced a beautiful dance on the stage with me, was no longer there.

468
00:30:44,060 --> 00:30:45,880
She had forgotten

469
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:49,520
that there was a pitiful girl she was irrevocably tied to.

470
00:30:50,180 --> 00:30:54,540
Just like her, she had dark eyes,

471
00:30:54,540 --> 00:30:59,780
and soft hair and a satisfied smile.

472
00:31:00,570 --> 00:31:05,130
She had forgetten, that I am still here.

473
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:08,610
And I will never escape,

474
00:31:09,320 --> 00:31:13,840
as someone who has died in endless time.

475
00:31:19,140 --> 00:31:21,190
Did you take these?

476
00:31:24,230 --> 00:31:26,330
That's a breach of privacy.

477
00:31:26,330 --> 00:31:30,470
You should show those to Li Xuan. She thinks you don't love her.

478
00:31:30,470 --> 00:31:32,820
Leave me.

479
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:35,180
Leave me, now!

480
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:45,650
Ms Ge, people can't live forever in hate.

481
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:03,640
Did she take those photos by herself?

482
00:32:04,250 --> 00:32:08,640
She didn't admit it, but her reaction gave her away.

483
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:12,130
It's really stupid to let oneself live under a mask.

484
00:32:12,130 --> 00:32:14,500
Aren't you shamefaced to criticize other people?

485
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:19,940
If she cares so much about Li Xuan, why doesn't she work hard to restore their relationship?

486
00:32:19,940 --> 00:32:25,090
In my opinion, she doesn't want to involve  Li Xuan into the war between her and her husband.

487
00:32:25,090 --> 00:32:29,530
Therefore, the only way is to make her stay out of the situation.

488
00:32:30,580 --> 00:32:33,320
Following your line of thilnking,

489
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:37,770
if Ge Xue Hong shows the photos to Li Xuan, do you think she'll be moved?

490
00:32:37,770 --> 00:32:41,540
Ge Xue Hong definitely wouldn't show those photos to Li Xuan.

491
00:32:42,670 --> 00:32:44,540
That's what I think, too.

492
00:32:53,660 --> 00:32:56,510
Haven't you been wanting to see Li Xuan?

493
00:32:57,830 --> 00:33:01,030
- Photos? 
 - They are all in her PC.

494
00:33:08,840 --> 00:33:12,690
Is it true that, once the breast cancer cells metastasized,

495
00:33:12,690 --> 00:33:14,510
there is no hope?

496
00:33:14,510 --> 00:33:19,250
That's right. Once they are metastasized, even if they are removed,

497
00:33:19,250 --> 00:33:21,780
death is only delayed by chemotherapy.

498
00:33:42,470 --> 00:33:44,790
- Miss. 
 - Did you get it?

499
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:47,350
I sneaked it out.  Madam doesn't know.

500
00:33:47,350 --> 00:33:49,720
Don't worry. This matter has nothing to do with you.

501
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:51,710
- You can go back now. 
